metadata.name: Overflowing 000- Génnēsis
metadata.description:
Bee Hallucinations - Overflowing-  dawn of the beginning,  Génnēsis Piece. 
Exploration of a strange AI metaverse inhabited by bees, existing on the edge of conceptual dream.  
 As Bees use building blocks to construct their world, spell prompting steers AI toward symbolic creation of this world in the same manner. Hallucinations are result of experimental prompting between too much and too little input. Exploration of such inputs is a purpose of this art series. 
 Irl the artwork exists within blocks on chain thus the conceptual circle is achieved.
